{"tid":1257961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有好似照顧細路咁嘅另一半","createTime":"2019-06-26T00:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T03:40:46.000Z","uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd83cee7534148253fac41ff5312b8f28ed40cb0","tid":1257961,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T00:29:32.000Z","msg":"成日任<span style=\"color: maroon;\">性</span><br />\n成日發脾<span style=\"color: red;\">四</span><br />\n成日打橫黎<span style=\"color: orange;\">講</span><br />\n成日唔聽人<span style=\"color: gold;\">講</span><br />\n成日都唔知佢想<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">點</span><br />\n成日做埋啲多餘<span style=\"color: green;\">野</span><br />\n成日覺得世界欠咗佢<span style=\"color: teal;\">咁</span><br />\n成日唔理你感<span style=\"color: blue;\">受</span><br />\n成日唔問候下<span style=\"color: navy;\">你</span><br />\n成日唔體諒<span style=\"color: purple;\">你</span><br />\n成日忽冷忽<span style=\"color: violet;\">熱</span><br />\n成日失<span style=\"color: pink;\">蹤</span><br />\n成日搞鳩<span style=\"color: brown;\">你</span><br />\n成日搞興<span style=\"color: maroon;\">你</span><br />\n成日唔比你休<span style=\"color: red;\">息</span><br />\n成日咩都要管住<span style=\"color: orange;\">晒</span><br />\n成日唔比你出街唔比你去見朋<span style=\"color: gold;\">友</span><br />\n成日講有朋友得啦唔洗要佢<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">啦</span><br />\n成日一嘈交就講以為你好明<span style=\"color: green;\">佢</span><br />\n成日一嘈交就話你唔再愛<span style=\"color: teal;\">佢</span><br />\n成日你再唔點就死比你<span style=\"color: blue;\">睇</span><br />\n成間做多咗啲野博關<span style=\"color: navy;\">心</span><br />\n成日陰啲陰啲咁<span style=\"color: purple;\">黎</span><br />\n<br />\n但係無論中幾多十樣，你都會守護住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果件又中幾多樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581b91c6c65525ed752bf774e6c1696b1be10a93","tid":1257961,"uid":60434,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T00:30:15.000Z","msg":"去5p開post"},{"pid":"bf10c505ea9d79a9019a7a79ed0eb2aa7406c418","tid":1257961,"uid"